    <item>
      <title>受风暴和风险偏好影响，油价有望录得一个月来首周涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在风暴弗朗辛扰乱原油生产后，油价有望在一个月内首次周度上涨，风险偏好情绪席卷了整个市场，有助于缓解此前超卖的原油市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 23:28:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贵金属价格飙升，散户抢购芝加哥商品交易所微型黄金合约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/retail-crowd-piles-into-cme-s-micro-gold-contract-as-metal-soars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在黄金价格再创纪录之际，散户投资者纷纷涌入芝加哥商品交易所集团（CME Group Inc.）的微型黄金期货合约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/retail-crowd-piles-into-cme-s-micro-gold-contract-as-metal-soars</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 22:52:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：交易员考虑美联储降息幅度 美国国债上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周美国公布的经济数据好坏参半，令投资者对美联储下周的降息幅度产生猜测，导致美国国债价格上涨，美元下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 22:17:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
